7-08-11T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"2c67476aa35ee766a352d314e689de7bb5467c23","tid":355763,"uid":35885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:22:04.000Z","msg":"都唔知點解做毒撚都咁辛苦"},{"pid":"ada49441c956d0e3899f960aa24c77bd23b39dfa","tid":355763,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都唔知點解做毒撚都咁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n千奇唔好迷失作為毒撚既身份，眾人皆醉須獨醒，莫要俾世俗蒙蔽歪曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aaacf98f4ce700d7db5836a5a75e76d16702f36","tid":355763,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:30:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都唔知點解做毒撚都咁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n千奇唔好迷失作為毒撚既身份，眾人皆醉須獨醒，莫要俾世俗蒙蔽歪曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰啲叫浪子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毒撚係冇得揀 都係世俗嘅人"},{"pid":"32e965d1335d149b48d6f1dd29d6e103462b9bb3","tid":355763,"uid":84951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8420ba448019f76887825716cbb67b80769811e","tid":355763,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:46:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都唔知點解做毒撚都咁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n千奇唔好迷失作為毒撚既身份，眾人皆醉須獨醒，莫要俾世俗蒙蔽歪曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰啲叫浪子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毒撚係冇得揀 都係世俗嘅人</blockquote><br />\nd人鐘意偽毒 呻狗果類</blockquote><br />\n哩個時世開毒撚集中區應該會畀偽毒侵入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4aacb4bbe720af074d48fb9f15afe85a3419c7e","tid":355763,"uid":88495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:57:35.000Z","msg":"為何做毒撚亦是罪名<br />\n為何不轟烈是件壞事情<br />\n從來未察覺我每個動作<br />\n沒有聲 都有愛你的鐵證<br />\n為何苦不浪漫亦是罪名 為何總等待著特別事情<br />\n從來未察覺我語氣動聽<br />\n在我呼吸聲早已說明<br />\n甚麼都會用一生保證"},{"pid":"4ea590366415cd0539235cbe81334e8a4f71ee82","tid":355763,"uid":53978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:02:12.000Z","msg":"生而為人  我很抱歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66bd2383827db354efa75d5da789c584f9e9b663","tid":355763,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a4e748bd0383f363fe614efd37efcc86127406","tid":355763,"uid":64276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:13:53.000Z","msg":"巴打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟愈大愈毒 好似有埋人格障礙<br />\n好自卑好想死<br />\n點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb439793b5e9c0d131f38c1f38ec4ab252428c6","tid":355763,"uid":35885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟愈大愈毒 好似有埋人格障礙<br />\n好自卑好想死<br />\n點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好死呀<br />\n就算世界都嫌棄我地<br />\n我地都要發揮毒撚既功用"},{"pid":"542d62448d04919adf252dfea31f8cedc19e98f8","tid":355763,"uid":35885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都唔知點解做毒撚都咁辛苦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n千奇唔好迷失作為毒撚既身份，眾人皆醉須獨醒，莫要俾世俗蒙蔽歪曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你，我會加油架啦"}]}